<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{فَلَا صدق وَلَا صلى}</span> أَيْ: لَمْ يصدَّق وَلَمْ يصلَّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ يَحْيَى:</span> نَزَلَتْ فِي أَبِي جَهْلٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ محمدٌ:</span> مِنْ كَلامِ الْعَرَبِ: لَا فَعَلَ، يُرِيدُ لَمْ يَفْعَلْ.<span class="c5"> قَالَ الشَّاعِرُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(وَأَيُّ فعلٍ سيئ لَا فعَلَه ... ْ)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">أَرَادَ:</span> لم يَفْعَله.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>